description: One intake flow for every team — marketing, IT, finance, design, legal, data, and ops. Requests are categorised, routed to the right owner, assigned an SLA, and tracked to completion. Keep your project tools. Replace the five Google Forms, the Typeform nobody checks, and the Jira queue that became a black hole.
